            <title>[PIG-4686] Backend code should not call AvroStorageUtils.getPaths</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4686</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In AvroStorage, backend code should never call AvroStorageUtils.getPaths().&lt;/p&gt;

